title: Press Releases: Remarks at the Milan Expo 2015 (US Department of State)
text: ( Source : US Department of State ) SECRETARY KERRY: ( Applause .) Foreign Minister Gentiloni, thank you very much. Mr. Prime Minister , Commissioner Sala, distinguished guests all: Vorrei cominciare congratulandomi il ministro degli esteri -
